                    <span>I enjoy reading this book. Really. The reason I gave it the four stars is that there wasn't enough of them. Mostly it had stories from famous people that we already know on. What I wanted to read was from people who are not as famous. Who had a lot of things to tell. I pray there is a sequel.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Wealth of Knowledge - History's Truths</div>
                    <div>
